					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I used a really simple method to do sprite cycling:<br />Add 9*4 to the output address after every complete sprite in the sprite table.  When it reaches 0, you've written all 64 sprites.<br />This of course assumes that sprite draw order or priority doesn't matter at all.</div>

					
